Installation & Usage
Method 1: Cookie-Based (Recommended)
bash# Install dependencies
pip install requests selenium

# Download ChromeDriver (if not already installed)
# For Ubuntu/Debian:
sudo apt install chromium-chromedriver

# Run the script
python auto_login.py student123 password123

# Or reuse existing session
python auto_login.py student123 --reuse-session

# Or use password file for security
echo "password123" > .password
python auto_login.py student123 --password-file .password
